<p>I'm happy to see japanese illustrator / mangaka <a href="https://nitter.rawbit.ninja/hirokimafuyu" title="ひろき真冬">@HirokiMafuyu</a> (68y old) posting more of his works here &amp; on Instagram.<br>
Some of his books from my shelves : "Louise" (1995), "Etiquette of Violence" (2000), "Apples" (2019).<br>
